00:03:45.450 --> 00:03:47.740
What is this story?

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:51.210
The story is that look at this.

00:03:51.210 --> 00:03:57.310
This equation says that if you
want this to hold it better

00:03:57.310 --> 00:04:05.440
